#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Atacked00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If only these monsters didn't exist, I\n"
"could just take a nice, peaceful trip..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Atacked01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The monsters... <2.pa>Looks like there's\n"
"still some left."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Failed00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I might have twisted my ankle a little...\n"
"But I think I'm OK, overall."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Failed01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm in a little bit of pain...<2.pa> But I can still\n"
"walk, for sure."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "Guardian00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Run, quickly!<2.pa> A <3.se_co>Guardian<4.re_co> is coming\n"
"this way!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm on a journey, pursuing the legends\n"
"I've heard about dragons. If you're a\n"
"traveler like me...\n"
"<2.so>Well, you should know that this region is\n"
"full of monsters and is quite dangerous.\n"
"It would be wise to pass through quickly."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_00_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>This area is a dangerous region full of\n"
"monsters...<2.pa> It may be prudent to pass\n"
"through quickly before you're attacked."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What? Me?<2.pa> My name is Totsuna. I'm a\n"
"huge fan of pretty much anything and\n"
"everything related to dragons!\n"
"<3.so>A traveler who got lost in <4.se_co>Faron Woods<5.re_co>\n"
"said he saw a dragon-shaped river,\n"
"which made me really curious..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_01_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A traveler who got lost in <2.se_co>Faron Woods<3.re_co>\n"
"said he saw a river shaped like a dragon.\n"
"Such a thing piqued my curiosity..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You might find this a bit strange,<2.pa> but if I\n"
"could only ever think about dragons,\n"
"I absolutely would...\n"
"<3.so>You know, if you stand on the shore of\n"
"<4.se_co>Lake Hylia<5.re_co> and look at the sky, you can\n"
"sometimes see dragon-shaped clouds!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_02_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you stand on the shore of <2.se_co>Lake Hylia<3.re_co>\n"
"and gaze up at the sky,<4.pa> sometimes the\n"
"clouds look just like dragons!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (long)
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorry if I harp on too much about\n"
"dragons, but... Well, I just know they\n"
"exist! They have to!\n"
"<2.so>\"A dragon-shaped river doesn't prove\n"
"that dragons exist!\" they say...<3.pa>\n"
"Pffft! It doesn't prove they don't, either!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_03_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I...<2.pa>definitely believe that there are\n"
"dragons in our world. I'm sure of it!\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>People can claim they don't exist, but\n"
"that won't stop me from believing!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: set_colour (blue)
#. 7: reset_colour
#. 8: pause (long)
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm on a journey, pursuing the legends\n"
"I've heard about dragons.<2.pa> Since you're\n"
"a traveler like me, here's a secret...\n"
"<3.so>If you keep following the <4.se_co>Faron Highroad<5.re_co>\n"
"to the east, you'll reach <6.se_co>Lurelin Village<7.re_co>.\n"
"The fish there... <8.pa>So good!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
#. 7: pause (short)
#. 8: pause (short)
msgctxt "MSG_Firo_04_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you keep following the <2.se_co>Faron Highroad<3.re_co>\n"
"east,<4.pa> you will reach <5.se_co>Lurelin Village<6.re_co>.\n"
"The fish there are just<7.pa> so <8.pa>good."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near00"
msgid "<1.so>Oh, the dragons..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near01"
msgid "<1.so>I know dragons exist..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near02"
msgid "<1.so>Where are the dragons?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near03"
msgid "<1.so>I want to see a dragon..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near04"
msgid "<1.so>It's started raining..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (long)
msgctxt "Rest_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>My head is always so wrapped up in\n"
"dragon stuff, I sometimes worry that I\n"
"might be a little obsessed...\n"
"Oh!<2.pa> Have you ever noticed how, be it\n"
"clouds in the sky, rivers in the forest, or\n"
"lightning...<3.pa>everything looks dragony?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Rest_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When it's all rainy outside, I like to let my\n"
"imagination run wild with thoughts of all\n"
"the dragon stories I've heard."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Rest_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's always so rainy along the <2.se_co>Faron\n"
"Highroad<3.re_co>... It's enough to make\n"
"travelers like us cry, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've been compelled to wander the land,\n"
"searching for the dragons I've heard\n"
"so much about.<2.pa> Let me tell you, though...\n"
"<3.so>This region is full of monsters and is\n"
"quite dangerous. It would be wise to\n"
"pass through quickly."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_00_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>This area is a dangerous region full of\n"
"monsters.<2.pa> It'd be wise to pass through\n"
"quickly, before you're attacked."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (10f)
#. 4: pause (10f)
#. 5: pause (10f)
#. 6: set_colour (blue)
#. 7: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I may not be showing it outwardly, but\n"
"I'm really quite excited. This place just\n"
"supports dragon theory so well!\n"
"<2.so>Lightning in the sky...<3.pa> Rivers winding\n"
"through the landscape...<4.pa> Almost like they\n"
"were carved...<5.pa> <6.se_co>Faron<7.re_co> is amazing!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_01_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The scenery of <2.se_co>Faron<3.re_co> is just so perfect\n"
"for the legends surrounding dragons.\n"
"It all but confirms their existence!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What? Me?<2.pa> My name is Totsuna. I'm a\n"
"huge fan of pretty much anything and\n"
"everything related to dragons!\n"
"<3.so>I had a strange feeling when I was near\n"
"<4.se_co>Lake Floria<5.re_co>... It felt exactly like how I'd\n"
"imagine being near a dragon would feel!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_02_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I had a strange feeling when I was near\n"
"<2.se_co>Lake Floria<3.re_co>... It felt exactly like how I'd\n"
"imagine being near a dragon would feel!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I want to see one in person, not just in\n"
"my dreams... <2.pa>Oh! I was just talking about\n"
"dragons...\n"
"People who've claimed to have seen a\n"
"dragon have said that the dragon\n"
"appeared to them at night..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_03_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>According to travelers who've spotted a\n"
"dragon,<2.pa> they all say they saw the\n"
"dragon at night..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whether this story is true or not is\n"
"anyone's guess,<2.pa> but it relates to\n"
"dragons, so I love it all the same...\n"
"Apparently shooting a dragon with an\n"
"arrow will knock a scale free from its\n"
"body, and that scale can heal any illness."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "RetMSG_Firo_04_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>They say if you shoot an arrow at a\n"
"dragon, you'll get a scale that can heal\n"
"any kind of sickness..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv1_00"
msgid "<1.so>Are...<2.pa> Are the monsters gone?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv1_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>So even the monsters are desperately\n"
"trying to survive..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv2_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If I were to get injured here, I might not\n"
"be able to continue my travels..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv2_01"
msgid "<1.so>Were you injured?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv3_00"
msgid "<1.so>That was scary...<2.pa> Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv3_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I don't know what else to say except...\n"
"<2.pa>Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Thanks00"
msgid "<1.so>Here...<2.pa> This is a thank-you for saving me."
msgstr ""

